{"tid":2508892,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[hotdog] 歐盟斥中俄不實資訊破壞歐美新冠疫苗信任","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:21:44.000Z","uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fd2a215f96527b9536ad9036b44fc46b050515","tid":2508892,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"歐盟發表報告, 指中國及俄羅斯有系統地, 嘗試破壞各界對歐美新冠病毒疫苗的信任, 不實資訊的目的是分化西方. 中俄都否認歐盟的指控.<br />\n<br />\n     歐盟對外事務部的不實資訊研究小組發布的報告指, 自去年12月至今年4月, 中俄國營媒體在網路上推出多種語言的假新聞, 大肆渲染疫苗安全疑慮、 無根據地宣稱疫苗和歐洲死亡案例有關, 同時宣傳中俄疫苗的好處.<br />\n<br />\n    路透社報道, 歐盟為阻止假消息散播, 除了試圖與谷歌、 臉書、Twitter、 微軟等科技巨頭合作, 並定期發表研究報告.<br />\n<br />\n    報告又提到, 阿斯利康疫苗及強生疫苗, 出現非常罕見的副作用, 都被用作大作文章, 認為中俄的疫苗外交以零和遊戲邏輯, 結合不實資訊和操縱行為, 破壞外界對西方製疫苗的信心."},{"pid":"db88deb43b377c42fca3c4c089cd983d275fe88e","tid":2508892,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20210429115553&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20210429115553%26page%3D0&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=f047259a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20210429115553&amp;page=0</a>"},{"pid":"06c3603c4e410bf6dc5ef32d1756d390eda4acbc","tid":2508892,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭🌭"},{"pid":"1887ec3f1e0a63b96c42131be8d65ad296cfcc76","tid":2508892,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4804f4bd9ae4c11fb015f7ccb22c2ddd7ca61f76","tid":2508892,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"之那說2億打科興⋯⋯冇人死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" 